<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="bg-[#080c14] scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us — ModelMatch</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/icon.png" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #f0f4ff; }
    .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #080c14; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #1e2d40; border-radius: 3px; }
    .card { background: #0f1521; border: 1px solid #1e2d40; border-radius: 8px; }
    .label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #64748b; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
  <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-[#080c14]/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-[#1e2d40]">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 h-14 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer" onclick="window.location.href='/'">
        <img src="/icon.png" alt="ModelMatch" class="h-7 w-auto" />
        <div class="font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">
          <span class="text-white">Model</span><span class="text-[#4f7eff]">Match</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="flex-1 max-w-[680px] mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white">About ModelMatch</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] mt-2">Helping you choose the right AI model.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">With hundreds of AI models available, choosing the right one for your task has become overwhelming. ModelMatch simplifies this by providing instant, objective comparisons tailored to your specific use case — whether you're coding, writing, researching, or creating.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">How It Works</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">Select any two models, pick your purpose, and our AI analyzes benchmark data, performance metrics, and known characteristics to deliver a clear side-by-side comparison with a recommended winner and a detailed verdict.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">What We Cover</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">We evaluate models across eight key purposes: coding, writing, research, logic/math, general chat, data analysis, image generation, and video generation. Our database includes models from OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Meta, DeepSeek, Mistral, xAI, and more.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Why Free?</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed">ModelMatch is built to be a public resource. We believe informed decisions should be accessible to everyone — no sign-ups, no paywalls, no data collection.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="py-12 border-t border-[#1e2d40] text-center space-y-2">
    <div class="text-[11px] font-medium text-[#334155] uppercase tracking-widest">
      abdullah systems
    </div>
    <div class="text-[10px] text-[#334155]">
      © 2026 ModelMatch. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
